{"type": "article", "id": 5075, "title": "吊脚床", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-09T08:13:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233722tyYxo4Aq9RZjXieW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t上班族、死宅族的福音来了。美国犹他州 Provo 的设计师 Matt 带来一款贴心的吊脚床，在你坐在桌前工作时，为你的双脚提供一个舒适且趣味十足的床。需要使用时，你只需将这款吊脚床用它配置的粘钩贴在桌面的底部即可。吊带的长度可根据个人需求进行调节，也可以拆卸下来进行清洗。提供网孔材质、绒面材质以及充电保暖款 3 种选择。目前，The Foot Hammock 正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，起售价 20 美元（约合人民币 124 元），<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/325876977/the-foot-hammock?ref=email\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>，预计今年 7 月出货。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/003/086/425/355a858ac7e87f5ef1599e05576c88e2_large.gif?1419802043\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/ksr/assets/003/084/529/9268e004fa91510255ab3a5a093db4ed_large.gif?1419719675\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052337197D9c4p1eIEr3iUHM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233720b0KIMcSrC7uxU3QJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233721INlxKO9qM0nv1Wse.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}